{"tid":1976183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"普京: 中國抗疫有效, 指責中國只會適得其反","createTime":"2020-04-17T05:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T19:06:32.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"70ba7af869545494c75e84d3913e6616e880ec40","tid":1976183,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:21:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200417/RVDBBZMSGMD5IUWK7WZF2TDUIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200417%2FRVDBBZMSGMD5IUWK7WZF2TDUIE%2F&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU98%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=cd805d0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200417%2FRVDBBZMSGMD5IUWK7WZF2TDUIE%2F&h=310eb989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200417/RVDBBZMSGMD5IUWK7WZF2TDUIE/</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】習近平普京通電話 稱指摘中國隱瞞疫情只會產生反效果<br />\n9小時前<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京與中國國家主席習近平周四通電話，兩人指其他國家指摘北京當局延緩向全球通報武漢肺炎疫情，只會產生反效果。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>克里姆林宮說，普京在電話中讚揚中國的「一致及有效行動」，令疫情穩定下來。兩人又強調對中國未有即時通報疫情的指摘，是適得其反。</strong>他們沒有直接提到美國政府。美國總統特朗普早前指摘中國沒有及時分享疫情數據，又表示將調查病毒的來源。<br />\n<br />\n中國官方新華社報道，習近平指把疫情政治化，損害國際合作。而普京指「一些人企圖抹黑中國」，是「不可接受」。習近平與普京又強調中俄兩國的戰略合作關係，表示會在疫情中互相幫助，包括專家交流及供應醫療儀器、防護口罩和藥物。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"8a104e06a632ef507b19b6160d3e45ac0ba94fd6","tid":1976183,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:21:52.000Z","msg":"英文source<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.france24.com/en/20200416-putin-xi-slam-attempts-to-blame-china-for-late-virus-response\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2F20200416-putin-xi-slam-attempts-to-blame-china-for-late-virus-response&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU98%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=c5a50298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.france24.com/en/20200416-putin-xi-slam-attempts-to-blame-china-for-late-virus-response</a>"},{"pid":"a9